<h2 style="font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Authentication Required</h2>

<p>A request was made to access your workspace. Please use the secure, one-time passcode below to authenticate your session:</p>

<div style="background-color: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 24px; text-align: center; border-radius: 6px; margin: 32px 0;">
  <span style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', Consolas, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #1e3a8a;">
    <%= @otp_code %>
  </span>
</div>

<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #64748b; margin-top: 8px;">
  <strong>Security Note:</strong> This passcode is valid for 15 minutes. Support staff will never ask you for this code. If you did not initiate this login request, please ignore this message.
</p>
